Class PMWebServiceController

java.lang.Object
  android.content.Context

                  com.panacea.sdk.web.PMWebServiceController
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2
public class PMWebServiceController
extends android.app.IntentService

This IntentService handles the initiation and response handling of all WebService calls. When the call and response handling is completed a a local broadcast is send via PMLocalBroadcastReceiver.

Author:
Cobi Interactive
See Also:
PMLocalBroadcastReceiver
